    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神秘的“愿望实现综合体”正在您附近建造，它们会将人类变成虚拟产品！</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>特点：</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >便捷易用的手机互动系统。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/74e9f301196836effd7e3e5d67fe6e80.poster.avif?t=1766020899\" aria-label=\"You use a camera app on your phone and interact with a coffee machine via a QR code.\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/74e9f301196836effd7e3e5d67fe6e80.webm?t=1766020899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/74e9f301196836effd7e3e5d67fe6e80.mp4?t=1766020899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在丰富多彩的环境中进行沉浸式模拟互动。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/a3670eabe3ee017f77ccfdaa64a4797b.poster.avif?t=1766020899\" aria-label=\"You enter a bathroom using your phone QR based HUD. You turn on the shower and the &amp;quot;disposal&amp;quot;. You then grab a toy from the hallway and throw it into the disposal.\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/a3670eabe3ee017f77ccfdaa64a4797b.webm?t=1766020899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/a3670eabe3ee017f77ccfdaa64a4797b.mp4?t=1766020899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这是一个功能齐全、基于同意的对话系统，它将为您提供一个独具特色、充满积极向上精神的个性化体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/8d0e6b28c9040d894f39ecbaec6545a0.poster.avif?t=1766020899\" aria-label=\"You are engaging in branching dialogue with someone who is telling you to take your medication.\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/8d0e6b28c9040d894f39ecbaec6545a0.webm?t=1766020899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/8d0e6b28c9040d894f39ecbaec6545a0.mp4?t=1766020899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>特权：</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供多种基于暴力的方式来缓解压力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/a006d4a14bbf7224581b5ed1a199a4c2.poster.avif?t=1766020899\" aria-label=\"You use a handgun to shoot at shadowy figures in a glowing, colorful room.\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/a006d4a14bbf7224581b5ed1a199a4c2.webm?t=1766020899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/a006d4a14bbf7224581b5ed1a199a4c2.mp4?t=1766020899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>经验丰富的操作员可在未公开领域获得高级职位（需安全许可）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/6293205888ac6aa26b8dd4887685aa11.poster.avif?t=1766020899\" aria-label=\"You are in a strange place that is very dark, throwing a light down a cliff made of stairs you reveal that goes down fairly far. The scene cuts to another dark scene of writhing creatures. You run away from them towards a glowing round doorway.\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/6293205888ac6aa26b8dd4887685aa11.webm?t=1766020899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248170/extras/6293205888ac6aa26b8dd4887685aa11.mp4?t=1766020899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>最低资格：</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >必须能够快速阅读。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >熟悉类似手机的人机界面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能够独立完成分配的任务。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>优先资格：</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有动力在没有正式培训或明确指示的情况下解决问题并操作系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能够承受心理压力大且没有明确解决方案的情况。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天生倾向于通过宣泄式、暴力的方式解决问题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强烈渴望创造价值。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抗耳鸣能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >道德灵活。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>重要系统披露：</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为最大限度地提高操作员的效率，将执行标准休息政策。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >偶尔的服务中断可能会导致系统出现轻微不稳定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在服务中断期间，遵守安全协议将确保您获得安全且可预测的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您在此模拟程序中体验到的任何恐惧都是真实有效的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前无法进行真正的人际互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>免责声明：</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*参与此独特机会需要付费。您的参与报酬无法以传统方式支付，而是将直接以价值的形式提供。</p>",
